OL,3,CSpecsavers co-founder dedicates royal
OL,4,Chonour to his staff
OL,6,FDame Mary was honoured by Queen
OL,7,FElizabeth II in 2007 for services to
OL,8,Fbusiness and charity, with Doug now
OL,9,Freceiving his own royal recognition.
OL,11,FHe says: "This award isn't really for
OL,12,Fme, it's recognition of the 45,000
OL,13,Fpeople who work for Specsavers and our
OL,14,Fophthalmic surgery business Newmedica
OL,15,Fand their dedication to changing
OL,16,Fpeople's lives through better sight
OL,17,Fand hearing.
