OL,3,CSpecsavers co-founder dedicates royal
OL,4,Chonour to his staff
OL,6,F"Together, we have achieved so much
OL,7,Fsince we began the business more than
OL,8,F40 years ago from pretty humble
OL,9,Fbeginnings and it's really quite
OL,10,Fincredible that we are now offering
OL,11,Four services to 48 million people.
OL,13,F"None of that could have been achieved
OL,14,Fwithout loyal, hardworking, visionary
OL,15,Fcolleagues and partners."
OL,17,FDoug was born in Llanelli, Wales, in
OL,18,F1943 and qualified as an optometrist
OL,19,Fin Cardiff just over 20 years later.
